snippet.title: World Turtles Strategy Game Trailer (Solo Indie Dev in Unity) Free Demo on Steam
snippet.description:
The trailer for my work-in-progress wholesome strategy game called World Turtles (developed in Unity) is ready.

Head on over to Steam to play the Free Demo!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1512050/World_Turtles/

Wanderer by Alexander Nakarada
www.serpentsoundstudios.com

https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

#unityrts #indiedev #freedemo
